{
  "texts": [
    "Legare (2017) reviews adaptations for teaching and imitation and their cultural representation.",
    "Mesoudi (2016) makes a broad review of findings in CES.",
    "Singh et al. (2021) review CES findings that, per the title, go 'beyond social learning'.",
    "Smith (2020) reviews theory and findings about cultural group selection.",
    "Tamariz (2017) focuses on cultural language evolution."
  ]
